{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/morph.png?t=1733060747\" />\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/chainsaw_flail.gif?t=1733060747\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Necromorphosis</strong>, the undead roam in an endless conquest to claim the throne of skulls and reforge the law of skulls and bones. <strong>You are a Skeleton,</strong> risen from your grave once more to challenge this never-ending civil war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choose your bones carefully,</strong> as you grow in power, feeding on the souls of the fallen. Here, only the strongest can survive, but even if you fall, heaven is not for you! Rise again, <strong>Skeleton</strong> and become the Bullet Hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625970/extras/logo__1_.png?t=1733060747\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Shape your Skeleton:</strong> Choose from weapons, arms, legs, skulls and assorted instruments of pain to craft the ultimate skeletal body.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Seek the Swarm:</strong> Endless hordes of nightmarish foes will challenge your claim, so stand your ground and take their strength for your own.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Search this Soil:</strong> Traverse through diverse maps to discover unique treasure, enemies, rulers, traps, secrets and even friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Seize their Supremacy: </strong>Defeat the merciless rulers who will test your skill and fortune, if you can prove yourself worthy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Survive and Survive:</stron